<p>Hey everybody, we're gearing up for another amazing year of learning, fun, and frenzied learning. The team has been putting together workshops, projects, and administrative work for the past few weeks. Right now we're kicking off with a pre-semester donations hosted on Piggybackr until August 31st! Help support us in expanding the team by funding our new learning workshops and cool projects. We want to bring this great project to more people by spreading the word as much as possible. We need your help!</p>
